{"tid":2304724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大噴鼻式新冠疫苗料下月至明年1月第一期臨床測試","createTime":"2020-11-29T05:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T05:17:00.000Z","uid":212249,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c67c365baa697e472a4672a0bca9b0d01133d3a8","tid":2304724,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港大學研發噴鼻式新冠疫苗，預計下月至明年1月進行第一期臨床測試，於本港邀請約100人，期望兩至三個月內完成。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學內科學系傳染病科主任孔繁毅：「我們已進入最後準備階段，我們正準備申請倫理委員會，即港大及瑪麗醫院的倫理委員會批准，下一步將向衞生署臨床試驗證明書。取得兩項批准後，我們會開始第一期臨床測試。」"},{"pid":"6780755ab69d267b8a4294220eca8d36c3eb316d","tid":2304724,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414690&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=e58ce5fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414690&h=6fa24a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414690</a>"},{"pid":"92af080e508618808b268bb99ad3ee05de4fc345","tid":2304724,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"第一期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}